# AUDIO::GET_PLAYER_RADIO_STATION_NAME

## Returns
* **STRING**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Gets the name of the players radio station. This serves as the text label.

Returns active radio station name
